---
---

<section id="vision">
  <hr class="neon-divider" />
  <div class="section">
    <p class="section-label">Creative Vision</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">The Future Is<br /><span class="accent-green">Spatial</span></h2>

    <div class="vision-grid">
      <div class="vision-text">
        <p>
          I see technology not as an end in itself, but as a medium — the same way
          paint is a medium for a muralist or celluloid for a filmmaker.  The most
          exciting canvas of our generation is <strong>mixed reality</strong>: the
          space where digital information is woven directly into the physical world
          we inhabit.
        </p>
        <p>
          My work sits at the convergence of <em>engineering rigor</em> and
          <em>creative exploration</em>.  I build systems that power immersive
          experiences — from real-time spatial anchors to GPU-accelerated shader
          pipelines — but the question that drives me is always the same:
        </p>
        <blockquote class="vision-quote">
          "How do we make a person <span class="accent-cyan">feel</span> something
          they've never felt before?"
        </blockquote>
        <p>
          Whether it's an AR layer that transforms a city sidewalk into an
          interactive narrative or a VR environment that teaches empathy through
          embodiment, I believe the next decade of computing will be defined not
          by screens, but by <strong>presence</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="vision-stats">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number">6+</span>
          <span class="stat-desc">Years engineering at scale</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number">AR/VR</span>
          <span class="stat-desc">Primary creative focus</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <span class="stat-number">∞</span>
          <span class="stat-desc">Curiosity buffer (never overflows)</span>
        </div>

        <div class="tech-readout">
          <p class="readout-header">// ACTIVE INTERESTS</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Spatial Computing</li>
            <li>WebXR / Three.js</li>
            <li>Shader Programming</li>
            <li>Generative Art</li>
            <li>Computer Vision</li>
            <li>Haptic Interfaces</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .vision-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .vision-text p {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .vision-text strong {
    color: var(--col-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .vision-text em {
    color: var(--col-neon-cyan);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .accent-green {
    color: var(--col-neon-green);
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.25);
  }

  .accent-cyan {
    color: var(--col-neon-cyan);
    text-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.25);
  }

  /* ── Blockquote ── */
  .vision-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.2vw, 1.25rem);
    color: var(--col-heading);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--col-neon-green);
    padding: 16px 24px;
    margin: 32px 0;
    background: rgba(0, 255, 65, 0.03);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ── Stats sidebar ── */
  .vision-stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .stat-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--col-border);
    background: var(--col-surface);
    padding: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--col-neon-green);
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--col-glow-green);
  }

  .stat-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    color: var(--col-text-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ── Tech readout ── */
  .tech-readout {
    border: 1px solid var(--col-border);
    background: var(--col-surface);
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .readout-header {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--col-neon-green);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .tech-readout ul {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .tech-readout li {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--col-text);
    padding: 5px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(42, 42, 53, 0.5);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .tech-readout li::before {
    content: "▹";
    color: var(--col-neon-cyan);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
  }

  .tech-readout li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .vision-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
  }
</style>
